WEBVTT

00:01.312 --> 00:04.457
It won't be easy carrying
your dead child to term.

00:04.483 --> 00:05.669
My baby.

00:05.764 --> 00:09.366
Jarvis finds a girl in trouble
with an imminent delivery,

00:09.367 --> 00:11.581
as soon as she goes into labour,
you're induced -

00:11.651 --> 00:14.703
and you emerge with a bonny
bouncing babe in your arms.

00:14.744 --> 00:18.690
I understand now why it meant
so much to you to learn about Anna.

00:18.776 --> 00:20.477
It's a miracle to me.

00:20.530 --> 00:21.898
They say your husband's alive.

00:22.063 --> 00:24.445
A photograph taken by my man
a week ago.

00:24.563 --> 00:26.565
Yes. It is him.

00:26.866 --> 00:28.146
I must go to him.

00:28.186 --> 00:30.951
I'd fight if there was a point,
but there's not.

00:30.969 --> 00:33.273
Gino and I have set the date
of our wedding.

00:33.357 --> 00:35.564
And you... are not invited.

00:35.778 --> 00:37.720
You're not welcome to stay again.

00:38.118 --> 00:40.947
<i>If it seems right,
you bring him home.</i>

00:40.982 --> 00:44.444
- I couldn't do that.
- If it's right, you have to.

